1. "Ona je popij*la sok iz flaše." (She drank the juice from the bottle.)
2. "Oni su popij*ali kafu u restoranu." (They were drinking coffee at the restaurant.)
3. "Moram popiti* nešto, žedan sam." (I need to drink something, I'm thirsty.)
4. "Ona je popila* punu čašu vode." (She drank a full glass of water.)
5. "Oni su popijali* punu flašu vina." (They drank a full bottle of wine.)